  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">GGF funds will support Taller Ecologista&apos;s work in promoting and implementing Zero Waste projects, introducing agro ecology practices, and advocating for closure of all incinerators in the Rosario region and Argentina. The group will continue running public awareness and educational campaigns by publishing media materials, conducting workshops and events, and maintaining 3 informational websites (www.tallerecologista.org.ar, www.basuracero.org, and www.noalaincineration.org). Taller Ecologista hopes to strengthen and grow the network of Zero Waste organizations, engage experts and politicians in a dialogue on negative environmental impact of incinerators and propose better alternatives, and organize public support for better waste management and elimination of toxics.</narrative>
  </description>
